@page "/"

<PageTitle>PaycheckCalc — Paycheck Calculator</PageTitle>

<h1>💰 PaycheckCalc Web</h1>

<p class="lead">
    A paycheck calculator covering all 50 US states plus DC using 2026 tax tables.
    Powered by <strong>PaycheckCalc.Core</strong> running entirely in your browser via
    Blazor WebAssembly — no server required.
</p>

<div class="card mt-4 mb-4">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">✅ Features</h5>
        <ul>
            <li>Gross pay from hourly rate, regular hours, and overtime</li>
            <li>Federal income tax — IRS Publication 15-T (2026) percentage method</li>
            <li>FICA — Social Security (6.2%, cap $184,500) and Medicare (1.45% + 0.9% surcharge)</li>
            <li>State income tax — all 50 states + DC with state-specific calculators</li>
            <li>Pre-tax and post-tax deductions</li>
            <li>Net pay calculation</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<a href="calculator" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Open Calculator →</a>
